{"tid":894700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PTU尖沙嘴港鐵站遇襲受傷　懷刀南亞漢被捕","createTime":"2018-11-08T14:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T17:13:34.000Z","uid":20933,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"75faa12117b3e81dc251a5f7bd3379088a4b306c","tid":894700,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"尖沙嘴險釀開槍翻版案。晚上8時許，3人在尖沙嘴港鐵站近A出口大堂爭執，有巡經的機動部隊人員上前了解，其間一名南亞裔男子突揮拳襲擊一名警員，同袍即上前將他制服，同時一柄摺刀由該男子身上跌出。該男子涉嫌襲警及藏有攻擊性武器被捕，其動機仍有待調查。受傷警員清醒，事後由救護車送院治理。"},{"pid":"bfdcf7dce302d4619b9d7d937d111b521c6fd1c1","tid":894700,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:46:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181108/s00001/858fff4ffbb297cd1ff615955186c022.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181108%2Fs00001%2F858fff4ffbb297cd1ff615955186c022.jpg&h=237e1d49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遇襲受傷的機動部隊警員，事後在醫院等候檢查傷勢。（伍浦鋒攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181108/s00001/85a0f949df17b725f435fdac4919332d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181108%2Fs00001%2F85a0f949df17b725f435fdac4919332d.jpg&h=fdb3baa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a43633b9624538d1410a0b4e13ac69fccf8891c","tid":894700,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:46:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181108/s00001/1541687961724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181108%2Fs00001%2F1541687961724&d=I%2BPZ7fZjwMgx79LWQpytRUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=65e4801f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181108%2Fs00001%2F1541687961724&h=f9eded97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181108/s0